		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am making a rom hack of SMB3 Lost Levels, and wanted to know the level pointer to make the World 1 castle into World 8 Bowser's Castle. I have tried SMB3 Workshop and level editor, and looking at various documents. I cannot read assembly, would someone be kind enough to help me find the hex offset for the world 1 castle pointer and what it needs to be changed to? Thank you for your time.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

